last_episode_to_air.overview: Freddie terrorises Rob with a jellyfish as the boys hit the road one last time. Freddie goes out on a BBQ bang when he serves up a bug banquet in the rainforest.

name: Freddie Down Under
overview: Travel Documentary hosted by Jim Carter, Freddie Flintoff is embarking on an epic new adventure travelling over 16,000 kilometres to Australia. The show has him travelling Australia with his sidekick - the journalist, extreme cyclist and tree lover Rob Penn - in a lime-green van called Flintoff's BBQ Joint, seeing the sites, meeting the characters and consuming some epic meals.
